_sText:
Install: Place gg_winterland.bsp in your C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\[Username]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.

Video of Map: http://www.xfire.com/video/3ff7f/

Recommended Player Size: 16-32
Maximum Player Size: 64
HDR Support: Yes
Extra Effects: Snowfall
